The maximum value of int is Integer.MAX_VALUE and the minimum value of int is Integer.MIN_VALUE.
A byte can store from -128 to 127. 0 is included in the positive numbers.
Float is a single precision floating-point type, with range of about 10^38 and about 7 significant decimal digits. 
short can store up to 65 thousand characters. 
